import React,{ useState } from "react"

export const Login = () => {
  const [email, setEmail] = useState('') 
  return (
    <form>
      <label for="email">email</label>
      <input
        type="email"
        placeholder="mokhtar@gmail.com"
        id="email"
        name="email"
      />
      <input
        type="password"
        placeholder="*******"
        id="password"
        name="password"
      />
      <button>Login</button>
    </form>
  );
}
